title: Reaction to Ryan Tannehill's New Deal & Calais Campbell's trade
itunes:title: Reaction to Ryan Tannehill's New Deal & Calais Campbell's trade
description:
DJ and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. On this show, the guys start off by reacting to the new deal for Tennessee Titans quarterback Ryan Tannehill (2:00). Next, they dive into Vikings QB Kirk Cousins' contract extension (4:41). After that, the pair discuss the Jaguars trading defensive end Calais Campbell to the Ravens (6:47). Then, the guys look into Cowboys QB Dak Prescott's contract situation (10:14). To wrap up the show, they react to the Titans placing the franchise tag on running back Derrick Henry (12:30).
